overview: On July 15th AAW pro Wrestling presents The Independents live on FITE. In the main event of the evening Mat Fitchett will face off the winner from Fred Yehi vs Manders in a match for the AAW Heavyweight Championship #1 Contendership Match.  AAW Women's Title #1 Contendership Four Way Match  Sierra vs Lady Frost vs Billie Starkz vs Vert Vixen  Shane Hollister vs Davey Vega  Tag Team Match  ??? & Silas Young vs ??? & Brayden Lee  AAW Heavyweight Title #1 Contendership Match  Fred Yehi vs 1 Called Manders  AAW Tag Team Title Match  Ace Perry & Alexander Hammerstone (c) vs ACH & Jah-C  AAW Women's Title Match  Christi Jaynes (c) vs Heather Reckless  AAW Heavyweight Title Match  Mat Fitchett (c) vs ???
title: AAW The Independents
